        <abstract> 
<p>Sends, with CD’s approval, a clarification of CD’s explanation of how useless organs might diminish [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9061</hi>]. Using Quetelet’s law of normal distribution GHD shows how horns of cattle, having become useless, would gradually diminish and finally disappear.</p> 
        </abstract>
